sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant UserController
    participant UserModel
    participant UserAccess
    participant Database

    User->>UserController: Register (first_name, last_name, email, password)
    UserController->>UserModel: register()
    UserModel->>UserModel: Validate user details
    UserModel->>UserModel: Hash password
    UserModel->>UserAccess: Save user details
    UserAccess->>Database: Insert user data
    Database-->>UserAccess: Data saved
    UserAccess-->>UserModel: User created
    UserModel-->>UserController: Return success
    UserController-->>User: Registration successful
